# Create README.md
cat > README.md << 'EOF'
# E-Commerce Platform - MERN Microservices

## Architecture
- **Frontend**: React + Vite (Deployed on Vercel)
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express Microservices (Deployed on Render)
- **Database**: MongoDB Atlas (Free Tier)
- **Image Storage**: Cloudinary (Free Tier)
- **Message Queue**: Coming soon

## Services
1. Auth Service - User authentication & authorization
2. Product Service - Product management & catalog
3. Order Service - Order processing
4. Seller Service - Seller management
5. Logistics Service - Shipping & tracking
6. Notification Service - Email/SMS notifications
7. Admin Service - Admin operations

## Getting Started
Follow the setup guide in `/docs/SETUP.md`
EOF
